I18n-with-scope
===============

This is a very simple plugin that adds a with_scope method to Rails' I18n module.


Example
=======

Instead of

I18n.with_options :scope => [:activerecord, :errors] do |locale|
  locale.t(:invalid)
end

you can use

I18n.with_scope [:activerecord, :errors] do |locale|
  locale.t(:invalid)
end

